WEBVTT

00:21.184 --> 00:22.464
ظآزThat dayظآز

00:22.880 --> 00:24.448
ظآزNothing stays together foreverظآز

00:24.448 --> 00:25.792
ظآزI've quit romanceظآز

00:26.218 --> 00:27.920
ظآزWho hasn't failed againظآز

00:27.920 --> 00:31.424
ظآزCrying in deathظآز

00:31.424 --> 00:34.016
ظآزAnd in lifeظآز

00:34.432 --> 00:36.370
ظآزEven nowظآز

00:36.672 --> 00:38.656
ظآزWe keep learningظآز

00:38.656 --> 00:39.680
ظآزIt's no surpriseظآز

00:39.744 --> 00:42.144
ظآزBeing happy is so hardظآز

00:42.144 --> 00:43.968
ظآزWeirdly, I became a role modelظآز

00:44.736 --> 00:46.688
ظآزOn the day we met again, we said hiظآز

00:46.688 --> 00:52.896
ظآزIt was a reminder,
a test, and a complaintظآز

00:52.896 --> 00:56.003
ظآزWho can do anything without regretظآز

00:56.003 --> 00:59.424
ظآزI am all rightظآز

01:00.480 --> 01:05.074
ظآزMay you live in peaceظآز

01:05.074 --> 01:07.456
ظآزLet the world roarظآز

01:07.456 --> 01:09.732
ظآزSounds like a carnivalظآز

01:09.732 --> 01:14.453
ظآزBeing alive is never dullظآز

01:14.453 --> 01:18.830
ظآزHow wonderful to be freeظآز

01:18.830 --> 01:23.485
ظآزI became even better without youظآز

01:23.485 --> 01:25.824
ظآزNothing can be perfectظآز

01:25.824 --> 01:28.224
ظآزWe bless each other in painظآز

01:28.224 --> 01:34.234
ظآزWe nod and smileظآز

01:35.328 --> 01:36.288
ظآزMay we both be wellظآز

01:36.288 --> 01:41.024
= Love's Ambition=

01:41.040 --> 01:43.952
=Episode 32=

01:44.058 --> 01:46.384
(Outpatient, Yuekang Hospital)

01:47.482 --> 01:48.322
Alright, Dad.

01:53.282 --> 01:55.163
Qu Mingcheng's land deal

01:55.523 --> 01:56.803
(Shouke & Jinda Accused of Bid-Rigging)
has been frozen by the authorities.

01:57.762 --> 02:00.163
There's no way to complete
the bet with the board.

02:00.322 --> 02:01.963
He will be in tough times.

02:05.083 --> 02:07.243
He's like someone sprinting

02:07.282 --> 02:08.402
who suddenly trips

02:08.882 --> 02:10.882
and falls hard enough to get dazed.

02:11.282 --> 02:12.162
When he wakes up,

02:12.162 --> 02:13.323
he finds himself

02:13.323 --> 02:15.043
tied up tight.

02:16.602 --> 02:17.602
All thanks to

02:17.682 --> 02:18.442
your cooperation.

02:27.722 --> 02:28.682
Regardless,

02:30.282 --> 02:31.442
I've always

02:32.002 --> 02:33.523
respected you.

02:33.722 --> 02:34.602
Well,

02:35.483 --> 02:37.442
we compete in business,

02:39.282 --> 02:40.083
but

02:40.763 --> 02:41.442
I genuinely

02:41.963 --> 02:43.562
hate seeing you like this.

02:44.643 --> 02:46.043
You don't need to say anymore.

02:47.483 --> 02:48.722
My dad can't hear you anyway.

02:49.562 --> 02:50.523
He's been unconscious

02:51.002 --> 02:52.162
with no awareness at all.

02:53.643 --> 02:54.523
Haoming.

02:55.923 --> 02:58.483
Your dad had
a sudden cerebral hemorrhage.

02:59.323 --> 03:00.722
This wasn't foreseeable.

03:01.442 --> 03:02.083
I also feel sad

03:02.562 --> 03:04.083
to see him like this.

03:04.722 --> 03:06.162
That's why I came to visit him.

03:07.402 --> 03:08.243
Are you done?

03:09.483 --> 03:10.763
My mom will be here soon.

03:11.043 --> 03:12.243
She won't want to see you.

03:14.043 --> 03:15.083
Alright.

03:18.243 --> 03:18.763
Well,

03:19.323 --> 03:20.682
take good care of your dad.

03:21.763 --> 03:22.842
If you need anything,

03:24.043 --> 03:25.523
just let me know.

03:25.882 --> 03:26.483
Bye.

04:01.323 --> 04:02.363
Who do you think

04:03.602 --> 04:05.083
acted better,

04:06.442 --> 04:08.122
me or Qu?

04:09.243 --> 04:11.442
Of course, your acting is superior.

04:14.043 --> 04:14.602
Careful.

04:19.763 --> 04:21.123
Before the bidding concludes,

04:21.842 --> 04:23.003
I need you to stay

04:23.482 --> 04:24.842
at the hospital a while longer.

04:25.523 --> 04:26.242
Okay.

04:27.282 --> 04:28.123
I'll do that.

04:36.162 --> 04:37.563
Having me hospitalized

04:38.242 --> 04:39.683
was to make Qu Mingcheng

04:39.683 --> 04:40.602
drop his guard.

04:41.083 --> 04:42.362
The board's bet with him

04:42.362 --> 04:43.482
was also your doing,

04:43.802 --> 04:44.323
right?

04:46.523 --> 04:47.963
Most importantly,

04:48.003 --> 04:48.963
most board members

04:49.123 --> 04:50.282
support you.

04:51.042 --> 04:52.722
I approached them privately

04:53.003 --> 04:54.323
with the proposal,

04:54.602 --> 04:55.523
and they agreed.

04:56.042 --> 04:56.802
But

04:58.003 --> 04:58.883
one thing

04:58.883 --> 05:00.282
puzzles me.

05:01.763 --> 05:02.643
Qu Mingcheng

05:03.003 --> 05:05.003
and Huang Chuming's bid-rigging

05:05.162 --> 05:06.763
is internal information.

05:06.922 --> 05:07.683
It isn't something

05:07.683 --> 05:09.282
just anyone could uncover.

05:16.963 --> 05:18.123
Very good.

05:22.443 --> 05:22.963
Mr. Huang.

05:23.842 --> 05:24.842
Qu Mingcheng

05:25.402 --> 05:26.722
has been officially arrested.

05:28.242 --> 05:29.443
The Diamond Plot project

05:29.443 --> 05:30.602
involves massive funds.

05:30.683 --> 05:31.443
Qu Mingcheng

05:31.523 --> 05:33.162
won't escape legal punishment.

05:34.003 --> 05:35.123
This charade

05:35.402 --> 05:36.763
is finally over.

05:38.402 --> 05:40.042
Without your personal involvement,

05:40.563 --> 05:41.802
Mr. Huang,

05:42.362 --> 05:43.802
our plan to take down Qu Mingcheng

05:43.922 --> 05:45.323
wouldn't have gone smoothly.

05:51.683 --> 05:52.643
Mr. Huang,

05:53.563 --> 05:54.602
why did you ultimately

05:55.003 --> 05:56.523
choose to work with me?

05:57.683 --> 05:58.722
Frankly,

05:59.602 --> 06:00.763
you and Shen Haoming

06:00.763 --> 06:02.042
offered similar terms.

06:02.162 --> 06:03.443
But you have Jinda,

06:04.003 --> 06:05.922
so Shen Haoming stands little chance.

06:06.443 --> 06:07.883
I have one more condition.

06:08.643 --> 06:09.242
Go on.

06:10.282 --> 06:12.443
Beyond our agreed terms,

06:12.763 --> 06:13.683
I want

06:13.763 --> 06:15.802
the two companies you own
in Hong Kong, China.

06:21.722 --> 06:23.563
You're really asking for the moon here!

06:25.162 --> 06:27.323
This is my only additional condition.

06:30.203 --> 06:31.402
As you know,

06:32.523 --> 06:34.242
I spent years on those two companies.

06:36.802 --> 06:38.802
When you officially become Chairman,

06:39.042 --> 06:41.402
you won't have time
to manage them personally.

06:41.643 --> 06:42.963
Those two companies

06:43.083 --> 06:46.083
are crucial to
my development strategy there.

06:49.523 --> 06:50.083
Fine.

06:50.443 --> 06:51.242
If you say no,

06:52.802 --> 06:53.963
I won't insist.

06:55.362 --> 06:56.563
Are there other options?

06:57.523 --> 06:58.203
This time,

06:58.402 --> 06:59.802
I'll take risks with you.

07:00.443 --> 07:02.643
The compensation should
naturally be higher.

07:08.443 --> 07:09.802
You try putting.

07:12.763 --> 07:13.362
I can't.

07:13.802 --> 07:14.602
He's greedy.

07:15.203 --> 07:16.602
I should be greedier than him.

07:16.763 --> 07:18.083
That's how I gained his trust.

07:19.162 --> 07:21.563
Judging by the situation back then,

07:22.162 --> 07:23.722
he did hold the upper hand.

07:24.282 --> 07:25.842
Just one thing has always puzzled me.

07:26.643 --> 07:27.602
Why did you

07:27.602 --> 07:29.003
choose to trust me?

07:31.042 --> 07:31.683
Firstly,

07:32.323 --> 07:33.563
he dragged me into bid-rigging.

07:33.802 --> 07:34.722
He made a mistake

07:35.123 --> 07:37.003
from the very start.

07:37.443 --> 07:38.083
Secondly,

07:38.523 --> 07:39.763
you were generous,

07:40.602 --> 07:41.482
meeting my requirement

07:41.563 --> 07:43.083
for mutual benefits.

07:43.963 --> 07:44.802
Thirdly,

07:45.922 --> 07:46.963
I've done business

07:47.443 --> 07:49.203
for so many years

07:49.443 --> 07:51.323
and have seen many people and things.

07:51.523 --> 07:53.083
But I meet

07:53.203 --> 07:54.763
very few trustworthy people.

07:55.003 --> 07:55.963
In life,

07:56.402 --> 07:58.563
genuine sincerity matters.

08:00.323 --> 08:01.123
Haoming.

08:02.443 --> 08:03.402
I admire both you

08:03.523 --> 08:04.722
and your wife.

08:05.162 --> 08:05.922
I believe

08:06.402 --> 08:07.643
you'll go even further.

08:08.563 --> 08:09.203
Thank you.

08:15.563 --> 08:16.123
Yan.

08:18.402 --> 08:19.722
I just met Mr. Huang.

08:20.323 --> 08:21.042
It went smoothly.

08:24.323 --> 08:25.083
What?

08:26.362 --> 08:27.408
Fang Lei came to our home?

08:29.482 --> 08:30.003
Okay.

08:30.722 --> 08:31.563
I'll be back soon.

08:39.203 --> 08:39.683
Fang Lei.

08:40.963 --> 08:43.642
Why did you come?

09:02.043 --> 09:03.242
Look at this.

09:16.762 --> 09:17.522
I'm sorry.

09:18.122 --> 09:18.842
Haochen

09:19.482 --> 09:20.882
is not your child.

09:32.203 --> 09:33.642
I'm sorry?

09:37.882 --> 09:39.122
Speak!

09:43.362 --> 09:44.362
What's going on here?

09:48.362 --> 09:49.602
Explain this!

09:50.522 --> 09:51.242
Back then,

09:52.842 --> 09:54.563
my sister suddenly came to me.

09:55.602 --> 09:56.563
She told me

09:58.083 --> 09:59.122
she was pregnant.

10:02.722 --> 10:03.722
You are pregnant?

10:04.083 --> 10:05.242
Whose child is it?

10:06.043 --> 10:07.002
I don't know

10:07.762 --> 10:09.842
if it's Shen Haoming's baby.

10:11.882 --> 10:13.203
Are you serious?

10:13.963 --> 10:14.563
You and Haoming

10:14.563 --> 10:15.642
have already broken up.

10:16.842 --> 10:17.963
Yes, but we

10:19.963 --> 10:20.803
broke up

10:20.803 --> 10:21.722
just two months ago.

10:23.242 --> 10:24.403
Does he know?

10:27.283 --> 10:29.203
I can't confirm if it's his child.

10:30.283 --> 10:32.002
On the day we broke up, I went to a bar.

10:32.002 --> 10:32.642
Then,

10:33.362 --> 10:35.203
I met an ethnic Chinese artist.

10:35.522 --> 10:36.403
That night,

10:36.403 --> 10:37.762
we both got drunk.

10:37.882 --> 10:38.642
And then...

10:40.482 --> 10:41.002
But

10:41.403 --> 10:43.403
it really only happened once.

10:44.762 --> 10:45.803
Who was that artist?

10:45.882 --> 10:46.762
Where is he now?

10:49.963 --> 10:51.762
I didn't even keep his contact.

10:54.602 --> 10:56.122
What will you do now?

10:58.882 --> 10:59.563
Later,

11:02.122 --> 11:04.803
my sister came to you

11:05.722 --> 11:06.242
and told...

11:06.283 --> 11:07.122
Tell me!

11:08.283 --> 11:09.642
Why did the old paternity test

11:09.722 --> 11:11.283
prove that Haochen and I

11:11.683 --> 11:12.882
were father and son?

11:12.963 --> 11:13.683
Why?

11:18.443 --> 11:20.803
It was all my fault.

11:23.522 --> 11:24.403
I thought

11:25.563 --> 11:26.842
as long as you kept believing

11:27.563 --> 11:29.403
that Haochen was your biological son,

11:30.642 --> 11:31.482
you and I

11:32.482 --> 11:33.842
would never

11:34.403 --> 11:35.642
be separated.

11:36.443 --> 11:39.762
And being together would feel natural.

11:40.762 --> 11:41.602
It was me.

11:43.803 --> 11:45.203
After learning you

11:45.203 --> 11:46.842
wanted a paternity test,

11:48.122 --> 11:50.762
I replaced the real test result

11:50.882 --> 11:52.482
with a forged one.

12:33.002 --> 12:34.283
You're insane!

12:36.242 --> 12:38.122
I know I've been absurd and childish.

12:38.163 --> 12:39.762
Absurd? Childish?

12:40.362 --> 12:41.362
You're so selfish!

12:43.283 --> 12:44.882
I was scared.

12:45.122 --> 12:47.002
I know...

12:47.083 --> 12:48.443
I know I was wrong.

12:48.443 --> 12:50.043
I truly feel sorry now.

12:50.083 --> 12:50.882
I'm sorry.

12:51.203 --> 12:52.683
I hurt Haochen.

12:54.563 --> 12:55.043
Look,

12:55.642 --> 12:57.043
I'll go to Jinda right now

12:57.602 --> 12:58.522
and reveal

12:58.762 --> 12:59.963
Haochen's true identity.

13:00.522 --> 13:02.163
Then you and Mr. Shen

13:02.203 --> 13:03.762
can reclaim your board positions.

13:11.163 --> 13:11.923
Fang Lei,

13:13.283 --> 13:14.923
you're not even human.

13:17.163 --> 13:18.683
Heartless creature!

13:20.122 --> 13:20.963
Have you ever

13:20.963 --> 13:22.242
considered Haochen's future?

13:22.362 --> 13:24.002
What will happen to him?

13:26.122 --> 13:27.122
Haochen has finally

13:27.122 --> 13:28.283
seen Haoming as his dad.

13:28.563 --> 13:29.203
Do you know

13:29.203 --> 13:31.083
how hard we've tried

13:31.163 --> 13:32.882
and how much he's done?

13:43.803 --> 13:44.762
Let me make this clear.

13:47.362 --> 13:48.362
No one will

13:48.362 --> 13:49.283
hurt Haochen.

13:51.803 --> 13:53.362
He only stays with me.

13:53.923 --> 13:54.923
Got it?

14:03.722 --> 14:05.482
Haochen will always be my son.

14:07.722 --> 14:08.563
Yan and I

14:09.083 --> 14:10.083
are his parents.

14:11.642 --> 14:12.482
This home

14:13.923 --> 14:15.122
is Haochen's home.

14:18.563 --> 14:19.882
I know, I know.

14:20.043 --> 14:20.602
I know.

14:21.163 --> 14:21.882
I'm sorry.

14:23.002 --> 14:23.762
I'm sorry.

14:24.882 --> 14:25.963
I'm terribly sorry.

14:26.242 --> 14:26.923
Sorry.

14:27.963 --> 14:28.803
Sorry.

14:31.323 --> 14:33.602
I'm truly sorry.

14:33.923 --> 14:35.722
I'm terribly sorry.

14:37.323 --> 14:38.122
Forgive me.

14:39.002 --> 14:39.722
My fault.

14:40.803 --> 14:41.642
My fault.

15:07.882 --> 15:08.482
Hello.

15:10.403 --> 15:11.602
I'm Han Weiping.

15:15.242 --> 15:16.362
My business card.

15:16.963 --> 15:19.043
Currently, I'm working

15:19.163 --> 15:21.043
at a shell law firm as junior counsel.

15:21.842 --> 15:22.842
Contact me anytime

15:22.963 --> 15:23.963
for legal matters.

15:25.882 --> 15:26.963
What else do you want?

15:28.803 --> 15:29.762
Steve and Qu Mingcheng

15:29.762 --> 15:30.683
have gone to prison.

15:31.522 --> 15:32.683
You should be grateful

15:33.602 --> 15:35.043
that they discarded you early

15:35.083 --> 15:36.323
as their pawn.

15:38.403 --> 15:38.923
Waiter!

15:39.482 --> 15:40.163
Give her a glass.

15:42.642 --> 15:43.283
Are you here

15:43.283 --> 15:44.443
to mock me?

15:44.803 --> 15:45.323
Fine.

15:45.683 --> 15:46.762
Let's drink while you do.

15:47.403 --> 15:48.522
I'm returning to the UK.

15:53.923 --> 15:54.522
Go ahead.

16:01.043 --> 16:02.043
Come with me.

16:04.963 --> 16:06.683
I don't like enigmas.

16:08.043 --> 16:09.242
However, I know

16:09.842 --> 16:10.963
you're obviously a bad man.

16:13.043 --> 16:14.443
To keep you from hurting others,

16:15.403 --> 16:16.762
I'd better keep you in sight

16:17.882 --> 16:19.283
under my control.

16:28.043 --> 16:29.482
You have one day to decide.

16:41.242 --> 16:42.002
(Conference Room)
Haoming,

16:42.642 --> 16:44.842
though Qu Mingcheng is gone,

16:45.283 --> 16:46.642
your family's scandal

16:47.002 --> 16:48.043
severely damaged

16:48.043 --> 16:49.242
Jinda's reputation.

16:49.563 --> 16:50.722
Since you're proposing

16:50.762 --> 16:51.923
to return to the board

16:52.283 --> 16:53.323
and rejoin Jinda,

16:54.043 --> 16:55.323
we have a question for you.

16:55.642 --> 16:56.602
What tangible benefits

16:56.762 --> 16:57.842
can you bring to Jinda?

16:58.323 --> 16:58.842
Exactly.

16:58.963 --> 17:00.482
You can't enter the board

17:00.602 --> 17:01.923
(North Waichuan Project No. 1137)
without solid performance.

17:03.803 --> 17:06.242
My plan remains unchanged.

17:07.482 --> 17:08.562
Secure the Diamond Plot

17:08.802 --> 17:09.522
at North Waichuan.

17:11.123 --> 17:12.802
Jinda has already
lost the bidding rights.

17:13.403 --> 17:14.482
The original funds

17:14.603 --> 17:15.923
could be invested in my company,

17:16.002 --> 17:16.603
Xinye.

17:17.242 --> 17:18.883
Using Jinda's money

17:19.242 --> 17:20.482
to handle your own affairs?

17:20.802 --> 17:21.322
Well...

17:23.522 --> 17:24.802
When Xinye wins the bid

17:25.042 --> 17:26.322
and secures the plot,

17:27.002 --> 17:28.163
we can co-develop it

17:28.363 --> 17:29.322
with Jinda.

17:31.562 --> 17:33.042
We need to review

17:33.163 --> 17:35.082
the bidding proposal
and development strategy.

17:35.403 --> 17:36.562
I've prepared everything.

17:38.322 --> 17:38.883
Take a look.

17:38.883 --> 17:40.016
(Project Catalog)

17:40.923 --> 17:42.363
Before our meeting begins,

17:42.363 --> 17:43.883
let's welcome newcomers

17:43.883 --> 17:45.163
to Yan Studio.

17:47.363 --> 17:48.603
Welcome.

17:49.082 --> 17:51.203
The combination of Yan Studio
and botanical dyeing

17:51.322 --> 17:52.123
has increased

17:52.123 --> 17:53.203
tourist numbers

17:53.203 --> 17:54.363
in Gubei Town by 32 percent.

17:59.522 --> 18:00.843
Thank you all for your efforts.

18:02.403 --> 18:03.802
I'd also like to announce

18:04.562 --> 18:06.603
that Yan Studio's offline stores

18:06.643 --> 18:08.242
will be opening soon.

18:08.722 --> 18:09.603
I hope

18:09.603 --> 18:10.762
we will not only

18:11.163 --> 18:12.762
promote new Chinese-style clothing

18:13.322 --> 18:14.603
but also

18:15.522 --> 18:17.123
create more job opportunities

18:17.123 --> 18:18.282
through offline expansion.

18:18.883 --> 18:20.042
That's equally crucial.

18:20.522 --> 18:21.843
Now let's have Ms. Qiao explain

18:21.843 --> 18:23.242
our offline expansion strategy.

18:23.322 --> 18:23.802
Alright.

18:24.482 --> 18:25.403
Moving forward,

18:25.403 --> 18:26.603
we'll focus on

18:26.603 --> 18:27.762
our three-year plan.

18:27.963 --> 18:29.643
We plan to open

18:29.643 --> 18:31.443
50 physical stores

18:31.883 --> 18:34.082
and estimate that it'll create

18:34.082 --> 18:35.042
over 300 new jobs.

18:38.802 --> 18:40.203
Our marketing department will

18:40.203 --> 18:41.963
implement integrated promotions,

18:41.963 --> 18:42.762
online and offline,

18:42.762 --> 18:44.123
to elevate brand visibility.

18:44.843 --> 18:47.203
The summer-fall collection
will start soon.

18:47.363 --> 18:50.363
Let's wait and see.

18:50.482 --> 18:52.522
Come on, folks!

18:52.522 --> 18:53.403
I can't wait!

18:53.403 --> 18:53.963
You know what?

18:53.963 --> 18:55.163
I've been working so hard

18:55.163 --> 18:56.322
to walk the runway at home.

18:56.322 --> 18:57.203
Guess what?

18:57.363 --> 18:59.282
Some of our new colleagues

18:59.282 --> 19:00.363
are actually your fans.

19:00.363 --> 19:01.002
You know?

19:01.002 --> 19:01.722
They also want...

19:05.603 --> 19:13.242
- Do it! Show us!
- Do it!

19:20.890 --> 19:21.328
(Project Description)

19:21.328 --> 19:22.192
(Goals & Vision)

19:30.256 --> 19:31.088
(Goals & Vision)

20:03.923 --> 20:04.683
What happened?

20:08.802 --> 20:09.963
What did the board say?

20:12.363 --> 20:13.403
Rejected.

20:16.643 --> 20:17.322
Their reason?

20:19.482 --> 20:21.522
They had no issues
with the bidding plan,

20:22.082 --> 20:23.002
but they were

20:23.242 --> 20:24.802
rather dissatisfied with

20:25.322 --> 20:26.363
the development proposal.

20:27.163 --> 20:28.403
They considered it mediocre,

20:29.242 --> 20:31.683
lacking the creative highlight.

20:36.403 --> 20:38.042
If I fail this time,

20:38.802 --> 20:41.002
I only have one last chance.

20:50.762 --> 20:52.883
I know nothing about architecture,

20:54.722 --> 20:55.963
but take, for example,

20:55.963 --> 20:56.883
Yan Studio.

20:59.002 --> 21:00.762
When I established Yan Studio,

21:01.923 --> 21:03.322
we really struggled

21:03.762 --> 21:05.322
to find our brand identity.

21:05.963 --> 21:07.123
When I first showed

21:07.123 --> 21:07.802
my proposal

21:07.802 --> 21:08.963
to Jiang Liang,

21:10.403 --> 21:11.923
he completely rejected it.

21:12.843 --> 21:14.643
That's why we changed direction.

21:15.963 --> 21:17.282
I pivoted

21:17.282 --> 21:19.802
from pursuing perfect clothing designs

21:19.963 --> 21:21.963
to creating accessible fashion,

21:21.963 --> 21:24.322
the practical needs in daily life.

21:24.762 --> 21:26.042
It's this very shift

21:26.683 --> 21:27.762
that makes Yan Studio

21:27.762 --> 21:28.643
find something new.

21:30.282 --> 21:30.722
Yan.

21:30.722 --> 21:32.282
Do you remember

21:32.923 --> 21:34.282
you said that local governments

21:34.403 --> 21:36.002
placed great emphasis

21:36.163 --> 21:37.802
on cultural heritage and history?

21:38.643 --> 21:39.322
Sure.

21:39.923 --> 21:40.762
So,

21:44.242 --> 21:46.203
could I formally invite you

21:46.762 --> 21:49.522
to become the co-planner

21:50.002 --> 21:51.522
for North Waichuan's development?

22:00.643 --> 22:01.683
Show me your proposal.

22:05.363 --> 22:06.082
Here it is.

22:11.403 --> 22:12.163
Look at this.

22:12.282 --> 22:13.643
But many renowned developers

22:13.643 --> 22:14.482
have shown interest

22:14.482 --> 22:15.363
in this plot.

22:20.123 --> 22:21.363
Thank you all

22:21.683 --> 22:22.482
(North Waichuan Plot 1137)
for coming

22:22.683 --> 22:25.203
to our presentation on Plot 1137.

22:25.643 --> 22:26.123
Mr. Shen.

22:26.403 --> 22:28.282
Let's start with the project's features.

22:28.522 --> 22:30.482
Our previous rejection focused

22:30.603 --> 22:32.123
on this critical aspect.

22:33.242 --> 22:35.322
This is the main structure.

22:35.683 --> 22:37.482
The core design element

22:37.562 --> 22:38.923
revolves around the river.

22:39.363 --> 22:41.603
The kinetic water curtain technology

22:42.082 --> 22:44.002
will amplify the light-shadow effects

22:44.042 --> 22:45.002
very dramatically.

22:46.282 --> 22:46.923
Impressive.

22:47.403 --> 22:48.282
It's essentially

22:48.603 --> 22:49.843
an exquisite art piece.

22:50.683 --> 22:51.242
Mr. Shen.

22:51.363 --> 22:52.562
While we appreciate

22:52.683 --> 22:53.883
the main building's design,

22:54.163 --> 22:55.562
how can you guarantee

22:55.603 --> 22:57.203
Plot 1137 will

22:57.242 --> 22:59.322
become a first-tier development?

22:59.643 --> 23:01.762
Regarding cultural positioning,

23:02.603 --> 23:05.082
let's welcome Xu Yan,

23:05.683 --> 23:06.963
my special art director,

23:07.082 --> 23:07.923
the founder

23:08.082 --> 23:09.363
of the renowned Yan Studio,

23:09.762 --> 23:11.002
a Chinese-style brand,

23:11.443 --> 23:12.322
to present her vision.

23:13.443 --> 23:14.443
Hello, everyone.

23:14.443 --> 23:15.123
I'm Xu Yan.

23:15.643 --> 23:17.443
About the interior

23:17.562 --> 23:18.603
of Plot 1137,

23:18.722 --> 23:19.683
our preliminary plan

23:19.683 --> 23:20.643
is to increase its value

23:20.722 --> 23:23.042
through cultural events

23:23.203 --> 23:25.603
and art exhibitions.

23:26.643 --> 23:28.363
Traditional commercial complexes

23:28.522 --> 23:29.562
typically relied on

23:29.562 --> 23:30.443
international brands

23:30.443 --> 23:32.482
for core value demonstration.

23:32.722 --> 23:34.203
However, consumers have shown

23:34.203 --> 23:34.883
growing interest

23:34.883 --> 23:36.242
in Chinese cultural stuff

23:36.322 --> 23:37.443
and spent on it.

23:38.042 --> 23:39.443
So this reflects

23:39.603 --> 23:41.522
the resurgence of Chinese culture

23:41.802 --> 23:43.522
and the boost of national pride

23:43.562 --> 23:45.683
and cultural confidence.

23:46.203 --> 23:47.322
Over the past three years,

23:47.363 --> 23:49.203
(Art-Commercial Complexes)
the intangible cultural heritage market

23:49.203 --> 23:50.802
has grown annually by over 40 percent,

23:50.802 --> 23:51.722
reaching a scale

23:51.722 --> 23:52.603
of 150 billion yuan

23:52.603 --> 23:53.843
of market value.

23:54.242 --> 23:54.883
Last year,

23:54.963 --> 23:56.562
Chinese-style apparel sales

23:56.562 --> 23:58.322
surged 43 percent,

23:58.482 --> 24:01.322
while intangible heritage crafts sales
grew 60 percent.

24:01.843 --> 24:03.322
Elaborate on your strategy.

24:04.282 --> 24:06.163
Our core strategy involves

24:06.403 --> 24:09.562
introducing Chinese
intangible heritage brands.

24:09.762 --> 24:10.843
We've made three phases.

24:11.963 --> 24:12.963
Phase one

24:12.963 --> 24:13.963
focuses on

24:14.002 --> 24:15.722
traditional textile crafts,

24:15.923 --> 24:18.163
such as Su embroidery,

24:18.282 --> 24:21.042
Yunjin brocade of Nanjing,

24:21.123 --> 24:22.883
and Hunan embroidery.

24:23.603 --> 24:24.603
Phase two

24:24.683 --> 24:25.722
focuses on

24:25.722 --> 24:26.923
traditional craft brands,

24:27.163 --> 24:27.883
such as

24:27.963 --> 24:29.923
Yixing Zisha clay,

24:29.963 --> 24:31.203
Longquan celadon,

24:31.322 --> 24:32.522
and Henan Ru porcelain.

24:32.883 --> 24:33.802
Phase three

24:33.883 --> 24:35.322
focuses on jewelry

24:35.322 --> 24:36.883
and art brands,

24:37.522 --> 24:38.883
such as filigree enamel,

24:39.082 --> 24:40.082
(Jewelry and Art Brands)
filigree and inlay,

24:40.242 --> 24:41.082
and cloisonne.

24:41.403 --> 24:42.363
These kinds of brands

24:42.482 --> 24:43.843
all serve our purpose

24:44.042 --> 24:46.123
to create an intangible heritage zone.

24:48.522 --> 24:50.322
The mission of our entire project

24:51.282 --> 24:52.562
is to establish

24:52.562 --> 24:55.082
an economically sustainable community.

24:56.082 --> 24:58.722
We want these artisans

24:58.722 --> 24:59.843
to have

25:00.242 --> 25:01.082
a stable means

25:01.163 --> 25:03.403
of sustainable support.

25:03.843 --> 25:05.042
Moreover, we hope

25:05.522 --> 25:06.643
this area

25:06.843 --> 25:08.242
won't just be

25:08.643 --> 25:10.282
for a temporary festival event

25:10.322 --> 25:11.843
or a one-time exhibition.

25:12.282 --> 25:13.683
Instead, we want people

25:13.923 --> 25:15.123
to live here

25:15.522 --> 25:16.562
and work here.

25:17.042 --> 25:18.363
So, they can

25:18.522 --> 25:20.722
feel a true sense of belonging.

25:21.802 --> 25:24.203
Regarding Jinda's investment risks,
how to mitigate them?

25:25.082 --> 25:26.683
My family's money

25:27.522 --> 25:28.802
will serve as junior capital,

25:29.603 --> 25:30.923
while Jinda's investment funds

25:31.443 --> 25:32.643
will be senior capital.

25:34.042 --> 25:35.762
You'll have priority

25:36.042 --> 25:36.843
in receiving returns

25:37.042 --> 25:38.403
but bear risks last.

25:39.282 --> 25:40.522
My goal is to minimize

25:40.522 --> 25:41.363
Jinda's risks

25:41.482 --> 25:42.282
as much as possible.

25:51.242 --> 25:52.443
After two and a half hours

25:52.443 --> 25:53.802
(One month later)
and 186 rounds of bidding,

25:53.923 --> 25:55.203
Xinye won the bid

25:55.203 --> 25:56.562
at 3.806 billion yuan

25:56.562 --> 25:58.242
for the North Waichuan plot.

25:58.603 --> 25:59.322
The premium rate

25:59.322 --> 26:00.603
reached 27.4 percent.

26:02.363 --> 26:02.923
Mr. Shen.

26:02.963 --> 26:04.163
What are your plans for

26:04.163 --> 26:05.082
Xinye's future?

26:06.002 --> 26:06.643
Well then,

26:06.683 --> 26:08.042
today marks a milestone

26:08.042 --> 26:09.443
for Xinye.

26:09.683 --> 26:10.562
I hope you will

26:10.562 --> 26:11.562
continue supporting us.

26:11.883 --> 26:12.562
Thank you.

26:12.883 --> 26:13.883
Today's meeting

26:14.002 --> 26:14.883
is significant.

26:15.322 --> 26:16.002
First,

26:16.482 --> 26:18.482
we'll withdraw the compensation lawsuit

26:18.762 --> 26:20.923
against Shen Jinsong and Shen Haoming

26:21.482 --> 26:23.322
and reinstate their positions.

26:23.562 --> 26:24.242
Next,

26:24.363 --> 26:25.843
we need to revisit

26:25.883 --> 26:27.282
the new personnel appointments.

26:27.963 --> 26:30.322
Currently, Jinda and Xinye

26:30.522 --> 26:33.163
have successfully
signed the acquisition agreement

26:33.683 --> 26:34.722
to jointly develop

26:34.802 --> 26:37.242
Plot 1137 in North Waichuan.

26:37.883 --> 26:39.802
Haoming played a crucial role

26:39.802 --> 26:41.203
in facilitating this collaboration.

26:41.482 --> 26:42.722
He has demonstrated

26:42.923 --> 26:44.242
exceptional management skills

26:44.242 --> 26:45.203
in project operations.

26:45.482 --> 26:47.363
We will aim to

26:47.683 --> 26:49.363
assemble a strong leadership team

26:49.722 --> 26:52.683
to oversee the entire project.

26:53.042 --> 26:54.403
After careful consideration,

26:55.282 --> 26:56.123
I propose

26:56.883 --> 26:59.562
that Haoming formally join the board

26:59.843 --> 27:02.683
and be promoted
to President of Jinda Group.

27:03.123 --> 27:04.562
Please raise your hand if you agree.

27:21.843 --> 27:22.403
Good.

27:22.643 --> 27:23.643
Unanimously approved.

27:24.002 --> 27:25.123
Congratulations, Haoming.

27:26.403 --> 27:27.683
Thank you all

27:28.242 --> 27:30.042
for your support and trust.

27:30.643 --> 27:31.363
Thank you all.

27:31.883 --> 27:32.443
Haoming.

27:38.042 --> 27:40.082
I hope you'll lead everyone

27:40.603 --> 27:41.562
and Jinda

27:42.403 --> 27:43.403
to a better future.

27:44.603 --> 27:45.242
Chairman,

27:46.002 --> 27:47.562
I'll spare no effort

27:48.242 --> 27:49.403
to live up to expectations

27:50.082 --> 27:51.242
from you all

27:51.363 --> 27:52.242
and Jinda.

28:18.683 --> 28:20.123
Add more filling!

28:21.082 --> 28:21.722
Grandma.

28:24.683 --> 28:26.443
Obviously, I made this one.

28:26.482 --> 28:27.963
And you made this one.

28:28.322 --> 28:29.883
Why does mine look like this?

28:30.762 --> 28:31.403
Yan.

28:31.522 --> 28:32.843
No matter how you make them,

28:33.082 --> 28:34.363
I'll always love those you make.

28:34.722 --> 28:35.643
I think

28:35.643 --> 28:36.883
Haoming will love them too.

28:37.522 --> 28:38.082
Definitely.

28:38.403 --> 28:39.242
For sure.

28:40.802 --> 28:41.603
Grandma, look!

28:41.843 --> 28:43.002
How's my dumpling wrapper?

28:44.042 --> 28:45.123
Not bad.

28:45.562 --> 28:47.363
You've improved so much.

28:48.042 --> 28:48.883
Haoming.

28:49.163 --> 28:50.482
Making dumplings

28:51.082 --> 28:52.562
is making wishes.

28:53.002 --> 28:53.843
Each dumpling

28:54.082 --> 28:55.482
is a blessing.

28:56.883 --> 28:59.242
You're rolling wrappers
bringing good luck.

28:59.802 --> 29:00.883
You're wrapping dumplings

29:00.923 --> 29:01.683
carrying wellness.

29:01.843 --> 29:02.963
And I am

29:03.762 --> 29:06.242
wrapping happiness.

29:08.683 --> 29:10.123
There's some insight.

29:10.443 --> 29:11.443
Did you read that online?

29:11.963 --> 29:12.923
Stayed up late again?

29:12.963 --> 29:14.443
No, I didn't.

29:15.242 --> 29:17.762
Look at these plump dumplings.

29:18.002 --> 29:19.403
They make me so happy.

29:21.482 --> 29:22.082
Plus,

29:22.363 --> 29:23.603
we are

29:23.722 --> 29:25.282
making beef dumplings.

29:25.843 --> 29:27.762
That means good luck!

29:27.802 --> 29:28.843
A family

29:28.843 --> 29:29.802
gathers like this

29:30.002 --> 29:31.403
to make dumplings,

29:31.522 --> 29:32.722
which means we will

29:32.762 --> 29:35.322
always live a happy and lucky life.

29:37.883 --> 29:38.403
Grandma.

29:40.042 --> 29:40.963
Look,

29:41.203 --> 29:42.603
if you live here,

29:43.042 --> 29:44.562
Haoming and I can eat dumplings

29:44.562 --> 29:45.923
every week.

29:46.843 --> 29:48.242
But if you leave,

29:48.522 --> 29:49.762
who will make dumplings for us?

29:50.762 --> 29:51.843
Why don't you just

29:52.643 --> 29:53.282
stay here?

29:54.322 --> 29:55.443
I've been here

29:55.482 --> 29:56.963
for a while now.

29:57.522 --> 29:58.443
But I have

29:58.443 --> 30:00.522
missed my garden plants

30:00.762 --> 30:02.562
and my little chickens and ducks.

30:03.123 --> 30:04.403
I had neighbors

30:04.963 --> 30:06.443
taking care of them.

30:06.843 --> 30:08.123
Your place is wonderful,

30:08.683 --> 30:09.762
really lovely.

30:10.883 --> 30:12.482
I'm happy to live here.

30:12.963 --> 30:14.482
But I still

30:14.963 --> 30:16.322
miss my own home.

30:17.443 --> 30:18.082
Well,

30:18.123 --> 30:19.282
I just want you both

30:20.123 --> 30:21.522
to stay happy.

30:22.082 --> 30:23.363
That's all I hope for.

30:30.242 --> 30:31.042
Wipe off the flour.

30:31.042 --> 30:31.762
What's he doing?

30:31.762 --> 30:32.163
Photos.

30:32.163 --> 30:33.603
Today's reunion dinner

30:33.923 --> 30:34.843
deserves a photo.

30:37.363 --> 30:38.562
With the dumplings?

30:38.643 --> 30:39.482
Sure.

30:40.082 --> 30:40.963
Let's take a selfie.

30:41.163 --> 30:42.002
Like this?

30:42.322 --> 30:42.963
Well...

30:42.963 --> 30:43.482
Is it okay?

30:43.603 --> 30:44.403
How should I pose?

30:44.482 --> 30:45.403
Just look here.

30:45.643 --> 30:46.163
Dumplings.

30:46.163 --> 30:47.683
One, two, three!

30:49.923 --> 30:50.403
Look!

30:51.318 --> 30:52.977
ظآزRushing toward the starsظآز

30:52.977 --> 30:55.036
ظآزUndaunted by painظآز

30:55.802 --> 30:56.443
What's wrong?

31:00.002 --> 31:00.643
See?

31:01.042 --> 31:02.322
- You look beautiful.
- Grandma.

31:02.722 --> 31:05.322
- Half your face is captured.
- No.

31:05.722 --> 31:06.443
Let me

31:06.443 --> 31:08.123
show you a magic trick.

31:08.562 --> 31:09.482
Watch.

31:10.762 --> 31:11.403
Ready?

31:11.963 --> 31:13.163
Come closer.

31:13.363 --> 31:14.082
I'm watching.

31:15.163 --> 31:16.123
What happened?

31:17.683 --> 31:18.522
What is this?

31:19.722 --> 31:20.123
Well,

31:20.203 --> 31:21.603
it came out from up here!

31:21.603 --> 31:22.722
What's going on?

31:23.482 --> 31:24.002
Magic trick!

31:24.002 --> 31:24.403
Look.

31:25.123 --> 31:26.163
Cover it like this.

31:26.482 --> 31:27.722
You teach Grandma to use this.

31:27.762 --> 31:28.522
Cover it.

31:28.522 --> 31:29.522
Abracadabra.

31:30.163 --> 31:30.883
It's magic.

31:30.883 --> 31:31.242
Cover.

31:31.322 --> 31:32.403
Cover it!

31:32.762 --> 31:34.042
- Warm it.
- Rub our hands.

31:34.722 --> 31:35.562
Okay.

31:35.562 --> 31:36.762
Time for the magic show.

31:37.042 --> 31:37.363
Alright.

31:37.522 --> 31:38.322
Let's give it

31:38.482 --> 31:39.802
some magic power.

31:40.562 --> 31:40.883
Good.

31:40.963 --> 31:41.282
Open!

31:41.762 --> 31:42.963
I can open it?

31:43.002 --> 31:43.643
- Yeah.
- Yeah.

31:43.643 --> 31:44.656
It better not disappear.

31:49.002 --> 31:49.963
Colors are emerging.

31:49.963 --> 31:50.963
Yes, colors!

31:52.123 --> 31:52.562
Look.

31:53.203 --> 31:54.322
Eyes in the photo

31:54.482 --> 31:55.322
look big.

31:55.322 --> 31:56.762
Manifest.

31:57.443 --> 31:58.242
Manifest?

31:58.443 --> 31:58.883
Manifest?

31:59.282 --> 31:59.802
What's that?

32:00.322 --> 32:01.203
Grandma,

32:02.042 --> 32:04.163
this is an instant camera.

32:04.203 --> 32:05.683
Grandma, your head

32:05.923 --> 32:07.722
is perfectly framed here.

32:08.843 --> 32:10.843
Great camera angle.

32:11.123 --> 32:12.403
See how happy we are!

32:12.762 --> 32:13.562
So happy.

32:14.106 --> 32:16.624
ظآزWhen I look backظآز

32:16.826 --> 32:20.712
ظآزWill you wait for meظآز

32:21.402 --> 32:23.318
ظآزLike fireworks that lovedظآز

32:23.683 --> 32:24.368
Grandma's asleep?

32:25.203 --> 32:25.762
Sure.

32:26.722 --> 32:27.482
What's that?

32:27.603 --> 32:28.443
This is

32:28.883 --> 32:30.163
my gift for you.

32:31.242 --> 32:32.722
Isn't this my photo album?

32:35.923 --> 32:36.482
Look.

32:37.482 --> 32:38.762
How old were you?

32:39.002 --> 32:40.123
I was 23.

32:40.336 --> 32:40.784
(In 2008, I was 21.)

32:40.784 --> 32:42.512
(In 2013, I was 26, and you were 31.)

32:43.962 --> 32:46.691
ظآزIf you remember meظآز

32:46.691 --> 32:50.096
ظآزThen I'm pleasedظآز

32:52.922 --> 32:58.192
(Today, we got married.)

32:58.192 --> 33:00.912
(Dad, Mom, and Kid)

33:01.018 --> 33:02.864
ظآزI love you, that's rightظآز

33:02.864 --> 33:04.176
ظآزHow I wish to say itظآز

33:04.176 --> 33:06.128
(Dad, Mom, and Kid)

33:08.250 --> 33:16.026
(Today's watermelon's so sweet.
Dad, Mom and Kid)

33:16.026 --> 33:19.760
ظآزDeep blue seas turn to foamظآز

33:20.122 --> 33:23.312
(Lucky wrapper, healthy filling,
happy folds)

33:23.610 --> 33:26.224
ظآزIf you remember meظآز

33:26.802 --> 33:27.363
From now on,

33:28.042 --> 33:28.843
this will

33:28.843 --> 33:30.002
be our family album.

33:33.242 --> 33:33.802
Here,

33:35.363 --> 33:35.923
here,

33:36.363 --> 33:37.042
here,

33:38.203 --> 33:38.722
and here

33:38.802 --> 33:39.802
will all be filled.

33:41.242 --> 33:43.714
ظآزI think by now you know itظآز

33:45.402 --> 33:47.335
ظآزAbout me and youظآز

33:48.163 --> 33:49.123
I'm happy to have you.

33:52.002 --> 33:52.762
Me too.

33:54.778 --> 33:57.758
ظآزRight now just to be here with youظآز

34:02.106 --> 34:02.832
ظآزI like youظآز

34:02.832 --> 34:05.267
ظآزHere in my armsظآز

